&lt;div&gt;As a Business Development Representative, you will be responsible for prospecting into target accounts to generate awareness and interest in Veracode’s application security platform. You will regularly qualify marketing leads and conduct discovery conversations with prospects and customers to understand their current security posture and the drivers behind their interest.&lt;/div&gt;
