&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage inbound sales requests received via web, email, and phone&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute outbound prospecting to build pipeline for Field Sales Teams using a multithreaded outreach approach&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage prospecting tools such as LinkedIn Sales Navigator and other outreach platforms to engage multiple stakeholders within target accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure efficient lead routing to appropriate sales teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review, contact, and qualify marketing-generated leads&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pass qualified opportunities to the inside sales team based on established rules of engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generate new business opportunities via phone and digital outreach, from initial contact through to qualified opportunity stage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with sales managers and sales enablement to maintain strong knowledge of Veracode’s products and value proposition&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with sales leadership and peers to refine messaging, targeting, and outbound strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate and timely updates in Salesforce,&amp;nbsp;ensuring all customer insights, activity, and engagement history are captured&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously develop sales skills, product knowledge, and market understanding&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
