&lt;p data-start=&quot;1193&quot; data-end=&quot;1523&quot;&gt;The ideal candidate is an experienced executive who has successfully scaled high-performing teams within fast-paced SaaS, cybersecurity, or technology organizations. This individual will bring a balance of strategic leadership, operational rigor, and a people-first mindset while aligning talent strategy with business objectives.&lt;/p&gt;
