&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We’re seeking a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Director, Strategic Product Management &lt;/strong&gt;who&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;will lead our software supply chain security strategy. This role requires someone who can understand emerging market and customer needs for securing the software supply chain for open source and other suppliers, and own the product business planning, product life-cycle management, and product plan execution for multiple products in Veracode’s portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll champion the user journey for developers and security teams who are addressing software supply chain challenges. You&#39;ll partner closely with our Product Design team to ensure user-centric thinking drives every decision, while working with our research teams to ensure that customers can navigate the emerging threat landscape with products that truly resonate with security teams, developers, and other stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a hands-on leadership role where you’ll be in the trenches. If you’re looking for a role where you delegate all the ‘real work,’ this isn’t it. We need someone who leads by doing.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will effectively communicate said product vision across functions to drive alignment and ensure delivery of business outcomes. You will serve as the stakeholder proxy to the Engineering team, helping our Agile delivery teams deliver features and functionalities aligned to a product road map. You will work together with other stakeholders to address internal and external workflows of the Veracode solutions, creating a strong user experience. You have excellent customer facing, Go to Market strategy experience, aligning with the Product vision.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
